latestIgtvVideos.title: This will help you understand
latestIgtvVideos.caption: YOU, yes YOU. You need to watch this. You need to understand. And once you understand the pain of systemic oppression BIPOC. You’ll take this link you’ll share it to your peers. And you won’t do it through lazy advocacy of social media performance art, you’ll do it by taking the time and texting it to people and start a discussion. White people listen to white people. #blacklivesmatter #icantbreathe #nojusticenopeace #checkyourprivilege
